      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a paper for my psych history class about the rise of the eugenics movement in the US and Europe during the early 1900s. I need to be able to explain the actual logic they used to justify their views on racial hierarchies. Could you elaborate on the specific scientific or social arguments those eugenicists used to claim that some races were superior to others? I need to understand their reasoning for my analysis.",
